Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.54,0:01:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,With high hopes, humans\Nleave Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.84,0:01:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...to begin a new life in\Nthe space colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.58,0:01:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But the United Earth Sphere\NAlliance gains military power...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.42,0:01:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...and in the name of\NJustice and Peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...seizes control of one\Ncolony after the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.73,0:01:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The year is After Colony 195.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Operation Meteor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,To counter the Alliance's\Ntyranny, rebel colonists...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.53,0:01:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...bring new arsenals\Nto the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.97,0:01:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...disguising them as\Nshooting stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.77,0:02:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Alliance headquarters\Ncatches on to this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty obvious that\Nyou're the bad guy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.43,0:02:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:24.93,Wing Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,717.75)\be7\blur6.75}Five Gundams Confirmed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.25,0:02:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been forced\Ninto a stalemate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.75,0:02:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There wasn't much{\i0}\N{\i1}we could do about it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...considering we don't{\i0}\N{\i1}know their objectives.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if we must act, the{\i0}\N{\i1}Mediterranean Sea's best.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where the old Leo\Nmanufacturing base is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The Alliance appears to be\Nthinking of added security.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.70,0:02:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't discourage them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.97,0:02:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I figured the Aries Middle East{\i0}\N{\i1}troops would be appropriate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.67,0:03:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Their ability to handle mobile{\i0}\N{\i1}suit combat is quite low.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So they probably shouldn't{\i0}\N{\i1}join the Alliance Military.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.94,0:03:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's written all over your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot them down for me, Zechs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So even OZ's latest mobile suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.40,0:03:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Cancer, was defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That suit's pretty advanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.03,0:03:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that wounded enemy's new\Nmodel that dangerous sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We've lost five good men.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.47,0:03:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Our loss is significant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are our next steps,\NLieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.21,0:03:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirm where the five\Nsuits are...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.91,0:03:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...and find out their objectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.55,0:03:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll leave this search to\Nthe Alliance's Marina.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.83,0:04:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy's no longer\Nin the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.53,0:04:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They've gone far beyond\Nwhat we predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They've succeeded in a mission\Nwe deemed impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Respiration 27, pulse 57,\Ntemperature 34 degrees Celsius.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.39,0:04:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Just thought I saw\Na fluctuation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue recording his data.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.38,0:04:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the treatment room\Non the 50th floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...of the Alliance Military No. 3\Nmedical building...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...in the South J.A.P. Area.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:04:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Major Sally, there's a call\Nin for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The disk you gave me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.63,0:05:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It has high level encryption.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't use any access code.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That kid had the disk on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So even the Alliance's mother\Ncomputer can't decode it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Think he's an intelligence\Nmember of the rebels?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too early to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in excellent physical\Ncondition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He has over 200 bruises\Nand broken bones...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...but his only visible injuries\Nare the shot wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious he's not just\Nany ordinary kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we use truth serum?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Careless drug use will\Npoison someone his age.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.36,0:05:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Also both of the pull carts\Nare broken...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...so have my lunch ready\Nat the back of the wheat field.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help you thresh\Nthe wheat later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I should go visit\Nthat patient!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.45,0:05:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's traveling as if it knows\Nwe're locked onto its position.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the one spotted at\Nthe Yangtze River.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's slow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.39,0:06:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging from its speed, flying\Nprobably isn't its specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There are different types\Nof these fighting units?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we'll see one of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...at the Corsica Base\Nin the Mediterranean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And even destroy\Nit then and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The one at the Yangtze River...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...won't show up at the\Nceremonies at Corsica Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It headed for the Alliance\Noffensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not as bad as long as\Nwe can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, the Indus Supply\NBase will be attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Pray they fight well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.34,0:06:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just so defenseless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not taking\Nme seriously enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No visitors allowed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are his injuries that serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're the one that\Nbrought him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here for one moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Major Sally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you tell me about\Nthat cute man you brought in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Cute man?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got no choice\Nbut to lie there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure a talented guy\Nlike you can read my lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Your acting is just amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:08:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You've regained consciousness\Nwithout increasing your pulse...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...or your brain waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a few questions\NI'd like to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're up to it,\NI'll help you break out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very interested in\Nthat young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a wild look about him\Nbut I sense an inner strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He's seems like just your\Naverage young guy to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.09,0:08:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.79,0:08:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Relena Darlian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Darlian?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Related to the Vice\NForeign Minister?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm his disobedient daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me if I said\Nsomething to upset you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I go see Heero now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.18,0:08:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.05,0:08:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a close friend\Nand classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Any changes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to report, Major Sally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.39,0:08:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you have him\Ntied down for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We're unsure of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's much too strong for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we've got him\Ntied down in restraints.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We have some questions\Nwe want to ask him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.80,0:09:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...then we can unbuckle him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not in the Alliance\NMilitary?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.51,0:09:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to liven things up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.39,0:09:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you get these off?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cut the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.33,0:09:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- You all right?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, release your parachute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you wanna kill yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have nightmares over this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.31,0:10:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They must've jumped from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Heero!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.47,0:10:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope he's not our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:11:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have released\Nmy parachute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.65,0:11:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand your wanting\Nto kill yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.79,0:11:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...but if you can't do it\Nfrom that height...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...then think of another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not asking you to\Ntrust me or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.83,0:11:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I'm the only\Nfriend you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:28.85,Wing Series Mid-Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(846,393.75)}Mobile Suit Gundam Wing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.65,0:11:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next we bring you the latest{\i0}\N{\i1}news from the military.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mass production of Leo{\i0}\N{\i1}mobile suits...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...at the Corsica Mobile{\i0}\N{\i1}Suits Factory...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...will resume at full capacity{\i0}\N{\i1}and without further problems.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The factory experienced delays{\i0}\N{\i1}after a mysterious explosion.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To continue the inquiry{\i0}\N{\i1}and for safety precautions...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...Specials from the Middle{\i0}\N{\i1}East will oversee the factory.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.41,0:11:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Zechs should\Nbe there by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:11:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back in two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I managed to make it\Non time for the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Bonaparte, it'd be\Ntoo risky to go in this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.47,0:12:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the best way to make\Nour intentions known...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...to the enemy and the Specials.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.21,0:12:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need the Specials\Nto help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll use this situation\Nto show themselves off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.65,0:12:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The Special Mobile Suit Troops,\Nknown as the Specials...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...advanced in the United Earth\NSphere Alliance Military...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Young leaders were trying\Nto start a new trend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Treize Khushrenada.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The aristocratic founder\Nof the Specials and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...an official in the mysterious\NRomefeller Foundation...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.31,0:13:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...financially backed by\Nroyalty and aristocrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,With this strong backing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...Treize focuses on the\Ndevelopment of mobile suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The Specials unit supplies\Nmobile suits to the Alliance...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.49,0:13:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...and starts instructing\Nthe combat army corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Their reputation on the\Nbattlefield is excellent...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.06,0:13:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...earning them the right to\Nact independently anytime...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...and at any battle they wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.83,0:13:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is no denying\Nthat this special status...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...angers the elder soldiers\Neven more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The men confuse the battlefield\Nfor an aristocratic game.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They want to kill so badly\Nthey're stirring things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We mustn't be persuaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If we proceed cautiously,\Nwe'll avoid unnecessary battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll teach those bloodthirsty\NSpecials about smart battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.16,0:13:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So Commander Bonaparte\Nisn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:13:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that he dislikes me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.54,0:14:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't really blame him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Zechs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Officer Walker, it's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.48,0:14:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed,\NLieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Got a machine for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna show you something\Nto do with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of the original\Nmobile suit models...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...and it's larger than the Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's outdated, but when I saw\Nthe data on Gundam...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...I thought of this unit; it's\Nseen as a historic artifact.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're from Corsica.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to work there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Only this machine can\Ncompare to the Gundam data.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.15,0:14:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't told how this\Nwas made, but we know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...that it'd have to be this\Nbig to maintain its power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.36,0:15:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It was too big...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...so the current mobile suit\Nsize became standardized.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tallgeese.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's what it's called.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.27,0:15:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This unit could fight the\NGundam if it were completed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it from this factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Counting on dying, Walker?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You taught me this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,..."to fight for the soldiers\Nof tomorrow."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've lived by that advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.85,0:15:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a braver soldier, Walker.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How many Gundams?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.02,0:15:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I expect the maximum,\Nas you taught me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There are four.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,One isn't headed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.03,0:15:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry Walker; that's\Nall I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.80,0:15:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be grateful if we\Neliminated one, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.84,0:15:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't, Commander\NBonaparte!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No enemies are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.54,0:15:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They ARE.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They are coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No one would challenge\Nthis security!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.13,0:16:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Specials, we'll attack at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.54,0:16:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Assemble!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only one unit's here, sir!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,One's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Descend! Descend at once!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one enemy unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Surround and destroy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not on the radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll check the monitor...\Nenemy confirmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't rely on equipment!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.48,0:17:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Strategically, when annihilating\Na small number of enemies...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's best to block retreat\Nand shower them with bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.39,0:17:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The commander's decision\Nto surround and destroy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...the enemy was correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.07,0:17:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He shouldn't have acted\Nwithout knowing my potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How could we have made\Nsuch a huge miscalculation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Assist retreat of the\NCommander's vessel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest, attack the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sir!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Given the enemy's strength,\Nwe won't make it out alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.46,0:17:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Give instructions to the Stats\NDepartment of the factory...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,For the soldiers of the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack up close and\Nstay focused!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.34,0:17:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The aircraft's ready;\Nyou can leave any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.04,0:18:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And Commander Bonaparte?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We received word of his safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Zechs, I'm going\Nthere too, with the Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Otto, I wish you wouldn't\Nmake this harder for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.52,0:18:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm about to convince myself\Nto protect the Tallgeese.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.23,0:19:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's out of bullets!{\i0}\N{\i1}We did it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay on guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll show you what the{\i0}\N{\i1}Specials are made of!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.21,0:19:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.34,0:19:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't afford a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That was pretty fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.98,0:19:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprise, surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.14,0:19:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Come get me, monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to find out\Nthis thing's limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.95,0:19:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master Quatre!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.36,0:20:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need any help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seems he's already used{\i0}\N{\i1}up all of his bullets.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.17,0:20:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That pilot isn't relying\Non any firearms.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No! There goes an OZ aircraft!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.54,0:20:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.65,0:20:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.22,0:20:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I shouldn't be fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.93,0:21:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your hands down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the first to surrender\Nand come out, remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.86,0:21:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There! I pulled up yours too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You could at least show\Na little gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.93,0:21:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.77,0:21:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.61,0:22:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He goes and puts a broken\Nbone back into place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.72,0:22:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That grosses me out,\Njust thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:31.37,Wing ED Lyrics,ED Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Maeburemonaku yobidasuno tenki ga ii kara\N{\c&H00FF00&}I give him a call out of the blue, just because it's sunny...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.88,0:22:39.12,Wing ED Lyrics,ED Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Watashi wo machiboukesasete nanisama no tsumori\N{\c&H00FF00&}But he makes me wait, how dare he treat me this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:43.79,Wing ED Lyrics,ED Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Hashittekitano wakatterukedo\N{\c&H00FF00&}I know he's out of breath from running here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.06,0:22:47.22,Wing ED Lyrics,ED Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Sonna koto wa atari mae yo!\N{\c&H00FF00&}But that's the very least he could do for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:53.79,Wing ED Lyrics,ED Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Just love! Kinikuwanai aitsu\N{\c&H00FF00&}Just love! He gets on my nerves...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.61,0:23:02.53,Wing ED Lyrics,ED Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Ijiwaru wo schichau no wa sukidakara yo\N{\c&H00FF00&}I only tease him because I actually like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.95,0:23:10.05,Wing ED Lyrics,ED Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Just love! Kininaru kara itsumo\N{\c&H00FF00&}Just love! I'm always thinking about him...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.12,0:23:17.49,Wing ED Lyrics,ED Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Murina koto itchauno chotto gomen...\N{\c&H00FF00&}Sorry I push things a little too far...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.36,0:23:21.19,Wing ED Lyrics,ED Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fs85.5\c&H00FF00&}Just love...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.06,0:23:30.07,Wing Next Episode Text,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,760.5)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Duo and Heero depart for\Nanother battleground.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.97,0:23:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Meantime, Wu Fei heads for the\NLake Victoria Base in Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,At the base are OZ's advanced\NTaurus space mobile suits...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.57,0:23:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...as well as Ms. Noin, an\Ninstructor of top pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.68,0:23:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There, Noin experiences\Na nightmarish incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.18,0:23:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, on Gundam Wing, Episode 4,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.09,0:23:58.60,Wing Next Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,715.5)\be7\blur6.75}The Victoria Nightmare
